Business modules
    Module:
        Manages individual modules which consist of sets of sentences.
        Among other things, it sets the current lesson and the number of displayed sentences
    Sentence:
        implements business logic related to:
            storing, sorting, modifying and deleting sentences related to user modules.
    Session:
        Combines individual modules into sessions.

Infrastructural modules
    Account:
        Create:
            create new account process
        Lifecycle:
            login,
            creating access and refresh tokens
            refreshing access tokens
            password changing
        Delete:
            anonymization account process
    Email:
        Sending emails to users
    User:
    store user data





